	<h1 class="title">在新加坡国立美术馆，愉快买买买也是正经事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113313/small/113313.jpg?1434099367" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马梦涵 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-19 07:00:38 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20875/medium/20875.png?1453104480" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="20875" data-title="《在新加坡国立美术馆，愉快买买买也是正经事》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20875/medium/20875.png?1453104480" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20875.html?hmsr=toutiao.io&amp;utm_medium=toutiao.io&amp;utm_source=toutiao.io" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
